Articles.Content:
Hi everyone! That's about it. My name is Jellotickles.

I know a lot of stuff about KSP already. I've already gone to Duna and the Mun. Landed on both of them too.

I launched a series of satellites all with the first letter of the planet and O.S, standing for object surveyor.

I've launched 2 of them by myself. One being the first satellite I launched, dubbed the Kuputnik.

That one hardly has any instruments, just 3 symmetrical communication antennas. The other one is the K.O.S

(Kerbal Object Surveyor). The last two is another one I just thought about that I launched by myself (with a regular rocket I

mean of course.) dubbed the M.O.S (Munar Object Surveyor). Last one I launched was the L.M.O.S. Dubbed the low munar object surveyor.
